casebody.data:
Mary Madeline McCALLISTER et al., Apellants, v. William H. MOORE, Jr., Trustee, etc., Appellee. No. 6457. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Aug. 29, 1931.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon consideration of stipulation of counsel for respective parties, and good cause therefor appearing, ordered appeal in this cause dismissed; mandate forthwith.
